#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.desktop.in:2
#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:7
msgid "FolderPlay"
msgstr "FolderPlay"

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.desktop.in:8
msgid "GTK;Music;Player;Audio;"
msgstr "GTK;Música;Reproductor;Audio;"

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:8
msgid "Folder-based music player"
msgstr "Reproductor de música por carpetas"

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:10
msgid "FolderPlay is a minimalist music player whose only purpose is to let you enjoy your local music collection by showing you the folders exactly as you have organized them on your disk."
msgstr "FolderPlay es un reproductor de música minimalista cuyo único propósito es que disfrutes de tu colección de música local mostrándote las carpetas tal como las has organizado en tu disco."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:11
msgid "FolderPlay does not group by artist, album, genre, or anything else… It respects the order you defined. It also has a strong focus on Lossless Hi-Res audio playback."
msgstr "FolderPlay no agrupa por artista, álbum, género ni nada más… Respeta el orden que tú definiste. También tiene un fuerte enfoque en la reproducción de audio Lossless Hi-Res."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:12
msgid "Features"
msgstr "Características"

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:14
msgid "Above all, simple and intuitive."
msgstr "Ante todo, simple e intuitivo."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:15
msgid "Displays your music folders in the exact order you have them on your disk."
msgstr "Muestra tus carpetas de música en el orden exacto que tienes en tu disco."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:16
msgid "Supports Hi-Res Lossless audio formats: FLAC up to 384 kHz / 32-bit, DSF / DFF (DSD) — DSD64 (352.8 kHz), DSD128 (705.6 kHz), DSD256 (1.4 MHz), DSD512 (2.8 MHz), and all other popular audio formats."
msgstr "Compatible con formatos de audio Lossless Hi-Res: FLAC hasta 384 kHz / 32 bits, DSF / DFF (DSD) — DSD64 (352,8 kHz), DSD128 (705,6 kHz), DSD256 (1,4 MHz), DSD512 (2,8 MHz), y todos los demás formatos de audio populares."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:17
msgid "HiFi audio output selector (PipeWire/ALSA) for passthrough with external DAC, or standard legacy output for compatibility (PulseAudio)."
msgstr "Selector de salida de audio HiFi (PipeWire/ALSA) para passthrough con DAC externo, o salida estándar para compatibilidad (PulseAudio)."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:18
msgid "Smooth folder navigation. Stores song metadata, cover art, and folder information in a local database — no disk reads required to display your collection. Populates the database in seconds and updates changes silently in the background, allowing you to manage large music libraries effortlessly."
msgstr "Navegación fluida por carpetas. Almacena metadatos de canciones, carátulas e información de carpetas en una base de datos local — no se requieren lecturas de disco para mostrar tu colección. Llena la base de datos en segundos y actualiza los cambios silenciosamente en segundo plano, permitiéndote gestionar bibliotecas de música grandes sin esfuerzo."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:19
msgid "Anti Bad Bunny feature: removes any Bad Bunny song from your collection (for the sake of your mental health). Let's promote real music! (Files are not deleted from disk — they are just hidden, in case you have a relapse...)."
msgstr "Función Anti Bad Bunny: elimina cualquier canción de Bad Bunny de tu colección (por el bien de tu salud mental). ¡Promovamos la música de verdad! (Los archivos no se eliminan del disco — solo se ocultan, por si tienes una recaída...)."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:20
msgid "Instant search by song, artist, or album."
msgstr "Búsqueda instantánea por canción, artista o álbum."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:21
msgid "Fluid adaptive UI for different screen sizes."
msgstr "Interfaz adaptativa fluida para diferentes tamaños de pantalla."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:22
msgid "Blurs the background color based on the dominant color of the currently playing track's cover art."
msgstr "Difumina el color de fondo basándose en el color dominante de la carátula de la canción que se está reproduciendo."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:23
msgid "Light and Dark mode."
msgstr "Modo claro y oscuro."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:24
msgid "Built following the GNOME Human Interface Guidelines, using GTK4, Python, libadwaita, GStreamer, GIO, and GstPbutils."
msgstr "Desarrollado siguiendo las Pautas de Interfaz Humana de GNOME, usando GTK4, Python, libadwaita, GStreamer, GIO y GstPbutils."

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:29
msgid "Developer name"
msgstr "Juan Carlos Bernal"

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:62
msgid "Browsing a Hi-Res FLAC folder in list view"
msgstr "Explorando una carpeta FLAC Hi-Res en vista de lista"

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:66
msgid "Grid folder view with cover art and adaptive background color"
msgstr "Vista de cuadrícula de carpetas con carátulas y color de fondo adaptativo"

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:70
msgid "Compact player view"
msgstr "Vista compacta del reproductor"

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:74
msgid "Adaptive narrow player view"
msgstr "Vista estrecha adaptativa del reproductor"

#: data/org.gnome.folderplay.metainfo.xml.in:88
msgid "First Release!"
msgstr "¡Primera Versión!"

